title: Smaller v1.3.8 [Zeus Downloads]
description:
Smaller v1.3.8
-------------------------------------------
Official Web Site: http://smallerapp.com/


Installation Instructions: 
------------------
- Open "Smaller v1.3.8.dmg" and Install the App.
- Open the Keygen app. First patch the app by clicking on the "Patch" button and dragging the app over the drop-down menu, then generate the license file by clicking on the "Generate" button. The license file will be generated on your desktop, Open it.
- Enjoy.


Important Note: 
------------------
- Don't update the app. You have been warned.
- If it says that the app is damaged. Then go to the System Preferences > Security and Privacy > General > Allow apps downloaded from and Select "Anywhere".
